      "job_description": "Leading Global MNC requires Manager/ Sr Manager - BD (Digital Loyalty l solutions) - Thane (Mumbai)\n\n- One of our client a leading Global MNC operating in over 80 countries and it is the world leader in employee incentive solutions & issuer of prepaid vouchers and cards. It is the leader in Employee Benefits, Citizen Benefits and Rewards Management business. Its products offers customers a secure payment instrument which can be used over an affiliated network while its programs helps its clients reach, distribute, reward, include and retain their partners, customers and employees.\n\nLocation : Thane - Mumbai\n\nSkills required : Should have a strong connect with the CMO's /Marketing heads in Corporates in Mumbai /Thane region\n\nJob Purpose :\n\n- The primary role is to Acquire clients for the Loyalty Marketing platform, which means connecting with Marketing heads / CMO's in Mumbai/Thane region\n\nKRAs :\n\n1) Business acquisition for Digital Loyalty solutions/ Cloud based platform\n\nPlease Find Below the details :\n\nClient : Global French MNC\n\nPosition : Sr Manager - BD ( Cloud SALES)- Digital Loyalty Solution Sales)\n\nExperience : 3- 8 years in BD /Client acquisition/ Cloud sales / solution sales/ concept sales role ( managing a large Business acquisition role in concept / solution sales )\n\n- Joining in 30 days ( one month)\n\nJob Role Vision :\n\n- You will be responsible for increasing revenue through new clients and contracts and generating new opportunities in cloud sales, loyalty marketing,\n\nJob Purpose :\n\n- Responsible to secure new clients & contracts to generate sales & revenue for Digital Gift Voucher in Loyalty Marketing, Product Promotions & Employee recognition programs.\n\n- Partner with Online & Offline channel partners, resellers etc.\n\nKey Result Areas\n\n- To achieve budgeted individual targets & collective targets of sales team for Digital Gift Voucher products\n\n- Generation of new database & mining existing database, market research, referrals driving.\n\n- Generate & Maintain strong sales funnel all the time\n\n- Strategic partnership or alliance with Online & offline channel partners & resellers to increase sales\n\n- To manage coordination with all internal support teams to ensure sales & on ground execution\n\n- Must have been exposed to corporate sales and solution selling with a good sales and marketing acumen.\n\n- Market study in terms of competition mapping, market intelligence and market share.\n\n- Closely work with merchant sales team to on board desired brand and product promotions\n\n- Mapping Industry/In depth verticals to ensure in depth coverage\n\n- To achieve budgeted individual and collective targets of the sales team for the respective products & services for India\n\n- To build the seeding database from internal and external data sources\n\n- Mapping industry/verticals to ensure in-depth coverage\n\n- Generate and maintain a strong sales funnel, Prepare customized proposal presentations to provide the strategy and solutions for various operative loyalty formats in consultation with the pre sales teams.\n\n- Conduct and analyze market studies in terms of competition mapping, market intelligence and market share\n\n- Keen market insight to preempt market needs and develop and implement strategies for new products and services accordingly\n\nRequirements :\n\n- The successful candidate will have 3- 8 years experience in a business environment, in a Cloud / concept sales oriented industry\n\n- Must have been exposed to B2B corporate sales and concept sales with a keen sales and marketing acumen. Specifically dealing with Chief Marketing Officers and Chief HR Officers will be an added advantage.\n\n- Ability to develop strong relationships to build either an industry or functional network\n\n- Personal and business maturity that leads to confident and rational business decisions\n\n- Demonstrated initiative and resourcefulness to develop well-planned strategies and achieve goals within tight timelines\n\n- Ability to manage a demanding workload, balance multiple tasks and switch gears while maintaining priorities\n\n- Negotiation skills, resource stewardship and an ability to handle chaos\n\nQualifications :\n\n- A post graduate degree is required, relevant graduate degree, MBA preferred\n\nPreferred Industries :\n\n- Sales and marketing (product and concept selling) with a strong marketing domain\n\nBehavioral Competencies :\n\n- Excellent communication skills; speaking, writing, listening. Articulate and persuasive; can communicate difficult and complex matters in a straightforward, transparent manner\n\n- Strong organizational, analytical, detailed planning and project management skills\n\n- Ability to maintain professionalism and honesty while building credibility, trust, and respect with both internal and external clients and customers\n\n- Ability to grasp concepts quickly, think beyond traditional methods to exceed client's expectations\n\n- Curious by nature\n\n- A team orientation will be a valuable addition to a collegiate, collaborative environment\n\n- Proactive and self-motivated. Action bias with a strong sense of urgency\n\nKindly confirm :\n\n- Your current ctc & notice period :\n- Experience in Cloud sales/ Solution sales/ corporate sales in Mumbai/ Thane region :\n- Revenue Target :\n- Ticket size of the solutions sold/ selling in the respective region/ territory :\n\n- Connect with the CMO'/CHRO's/CXO's in the respective market :\n\nAbhinav\n\n9548238406",
